name: PAC Protocol
public_notice: Pac Global (former) has been rebranded as Pac Protocol. For more info: https://twitter.com/PACcoinOfficial/status/1375130834118832133?s=20

description.en:
PAC Protocol (PAC), based in the US, aims to provide next-generation blockchain network solutions to solve real-world problems. It claims to be one of the largest truly decentralized masternode networks in the world (source: www.masternodes.online) with nearly over 13,000 active nodes located worldwide. Its network is based on the energy efficient Proof of Stake (PoS) algorithm which greatly reduces its overall carbon footprint.

For more information about PAC Global or if you are interested in partnering with the project, please either contact Drew Saunders, Chairman of the Board at drewsaunders@pacglobal.io or David Gokhshtein, CEO at davidg@pacglobal.io or visit @PACcoinOfficial or website at (www.pacglobal.io).

status_updates.description:
PAC Protocol Brand Guidelines

For our community and partnerships, PAC Protocol is publishing our brand guide to keep all of us consistent with our content that we create.

Download all of the logos, colors and more for PACProtocol brand guide!


pacprotocol.com/pdf/pacprotocol-brand-guide.pdf

PAC Protocol + Radiologex

One of PAC Protocol's largest partnerships is with Radiologex.
Using data storage from the PAC Network, R-DEE's platform is decentralized, immutable, fast and accessed in real-time for healthcare professionals.

This enables better care for the public with data that is trusted and secure, stored on over 1700 nodes.

https://twitter.com/PACcoinOfficial/status/1393326330687668228?s=20

PAC Protocol is excited to announce that it will be enabling PAC nodes to participate on the Flare network

PAC will structure a decentralized “Data Provider” on Flare that uses the PAC master node system to aggregate and submit price data to the Flare Network.

https://twitter.com/PACcoinOfficial/status/1392556811262185473?s=20

🌎🐶Node Validator🐶🌎

Decentralization is the power behind #Blockchain! 

PAC Protocol has added to the $DOGE ecosystem with a node validator! 

https://www.facebook.com/PACProtocol/posts/939720113512134

🚨Partnership update🚨
Being a partner with Flare Networks FLR means that we build each others projects. 

From node validators with $PAC to $FLR & supporting their redemption of assets on the #XRP ledger we move forward, growing technology together. 

Find out more by joining our communities.


https://www.reddit.com/r/PACGlobalOfficial/comments/mqap0e/flare_partnership_update/

📱PACapp Update Available Now📱
The PACapp has been updated with a new and improved version from PAC Protocol. Seamlessly manage your $PAC with our proprietary software on the PACapp‼

🌎Partners & Node Validators🌏



PAC Protocol is working hard with our partners and node validators to create value for our community and network every day. 



Watch for more information as we develop the next levels of these partnerships along with new ones. 

https://twitter.com/PACcoinOfficial/status/1380568016245624843?s=20
